room_title: Escape room "Survival" by Countdown Louisville in Louisville
room_description: As meteorites rain down on Earth you and your team are on a mission to help hackers intercept the one that could destroy the planet. Your group is divided, trapped in separate rooms!  If you can break down the wall between you and combine your resources, you may have a chance...The meteorite nicknamed Molly is spiraling toward Earth. With just an hour left before the apocalypse, will you survive?
